text: Žiga Zatežič (born 20 December 1995) is a Slovenian professional basketball player who last played for Krka-Telekom of the Telemach League. ==References== ==External links== * Profile at abaliga.com * Profile at eurobasket.com * Profile at kzs.si Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Novo Mesto Category:Slovenian men's basketball players Category:Shooting guards Category:KK Krka players Category:ABA League players
